data.description: Charming Spanish-style 3/2 sits on a spacious 1/3-acre lot in the coveted Northwood Hills neighborhood, mere minutes away from downtown West Palm Beach. Recently renovated, the home showcases a chef's kitchen with an inviting eat-in dining area and an expansive open floor plan. Throughout the interior, original hardwood floors complement lofty 10-foot ceilings, generously sized rooms, and a luxurious master suite complete with a private bath, walk-in closet, and gas fireplace. Additional highlights include a convenient laundry room, ample storage space, and a distinctive wine cellar. Large 13,000+ square feet corner lot offers fruit trees, a summer kitchen, a tiki hut, a covered deck, and a stone courtyard.
